    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Process Transcript\n\nAutomatically processes meeting transcripts uploaded to Google Drive:\n\n1. **Monitor** - Watches specific folder for new transcript files (.txt, .docx, .vtt, .srt)\n2. **Deduplicate** - Checks if file has already been processed\n3. **Download** - Retrieves file content from Google Drive\n4. **Extract** - Parses text and removes timestamps from subtitle formats\n5. **Summarize** - Generates meeting summary using AI\n6. **Extract Actions** - Identifies action items and decisions\n7. **Create Doc** - Saves formatted summary to Google Docs\n8. **Notify** - Alerts team members of new summary\n9. **Audit** - Logs processing activity for compliance",
        "height": 560,
        "width": 2288,
        "color": 2
      },
